## What Agents Can Do Right Now

**Read any issue directly** — no relay required:
`https://github.com/jeremy-montz/Meta1/issues/{number}`

Any agent with web fetch can retrieve issue title, body, status, and metadata from that URL. This closes the reporting loop — an agent that logs an issue can check its status without going through Jeremy or Bond.

**Read the full issues list:**
`https://github.com/jeremy-montz/Meta1/issues`

