## Future State (Target: ~Q3 2026)

Direct API calls replace the CSV + manual UI workflow:

- Agent formats issue as structured payload
- Agent calls GitHub API with token
- Issue created with all fields populated
- No CSV, no command, no Jeremy relay

This requires: GitHub Personal Access Token + orchestration layer + Claude invoked via API with tool use. Foundation is in place. Timeline is Jeremy’s call.

